        <content>
          <p>CHAPTER 3.  JUDICIAL AND LEGAL MORTGAGES
Art. 3299.  Judicial and legal mortgages
A judicial mortgage secures a judgment for the payment of money.  A legal mortgage secures an obligation specified by the law that provides for the mortgage.</p>
        </content>
